data.text:
We were pleased to welcome San Francisco's Mya Byrneto come and cut our 653rd Direct-to-Vinyl Live Session on February 7th, 2019. This session was available exclusively via preorder, which has now closed.

Each of these 13 takes were cut directly to their own individual 7" vinyl record, and only one copy of each take exists in the world.

Our limited edition lathe cut record releases are made on a modified antique record cutting lathe from the 1950's. Each record is handmade, one at a time, in real time, by a real person.
